title: Introducing The New Rampage Pro Carbon MTB Helmet
description:
When designing the new Rampage Pro Carbon we really focused on fit and comfort.

With four months of testing during the World Cup and FMB season, the helmet already has 14 podiums and our top athletes are very happy with it. Here is the edit to show you what went on over the four months of testing. Enjoy.
